{"tid":2203949,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"郭嘉銓: 膝壓12歲女童案已主動交投訴課跟進","createTime":"2020-09-15T16:42:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T19:02:52.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"41a5973b105ca86b1525a267ce30c0ce2466f9b3","tid":2203949,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T16:42:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/BlXZDiRX-eSmhDnWiVrbffZ5gRc=/802x1134/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PJT6QJGHCNDXLM3DTAQFQOS6V4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FBlXZDiRX-eSmhDnWiVrbffZ5gRc%3D%2F802x1134%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPJT6QJGHCNDXLM3DTAQFQOS6V4.jpg&h=ff296121&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n多名防暴本月6日在旺角街頭以騎身和膝壓制服一名12歲女童，引來多方炮轟。曾「死撐」是使用「最低所需武力」的警方，今回信教育界立法會議員葉建源時一改口風，不再提及有關字眼，又說已將事件主動交至投訴警察課跟進。信中稱，警方一直非常重視保護婦女及兒童的權益，而相關執法行動是基於「保障公眾安全和社會秩序而作出」。<br />\n<br />\n葉說，警方今日第二次的回信，態度明顯與第一次回信不同，不再傲慢和以高姿態指摘，亦無將回信放上警方fb，「感覺警方係想息事寧人」。不過，他指，回信還是沒有回應到多方的質疑，批評警方仍迴避交代真相，「係邊度（事實描述）唔全面？當時係咪使用緊最低武力？係咪濫用緊限聚令告票？全部無答到」。<br />\n<br />\n葉續指，警方主動將事件交至投訴警察課做法少見，認為當中有兩種可能性，「一係佢（發現）係有問題嘅，一係只係緩兵之計，咁佢就唔需要再正面回應大家嘅質詢」。他說，過去絕大部份投訴警察的成功個案極低，公眾不能因此而存有厚望，但強調港人眼睛是雪亮的，促警方盡快正面回應事件，還女童公道。而女童母親則表示，暫時不便再作回應。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200915/LZQLE52M3JC5BF5E4AIZ7LROGE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200915%2FLZQLE52M3JC5BF5E4AIZ7LROGE%2F&d=ulKCtXgG4rwmRR8qyGKIuZLdSN32AczdJcE5lfwVwJ8%3D&h=2ced0d31\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200915%2FLZQLE52M3JC5BF5E4AIZ7LROGE%2F&h=2b6917e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200915/LZQLE52M3JC5BF5E4AIZ7LROGE/</a>"},{"pid":"d442adec688bf3d500a96946a6280ae8a7f9cd55","tid":2203949,"uid":319935,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T16:42:45.000Z","msg":"開始做啲門面嘢"},{"pid":"979a543afb2a69130c6f6886c5c888aea478a8d5","tid":2203949,"uid":274532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T16:42:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e0c3374a4f96b15667a7d0654b815343a44e49e","tid":2203949,"uid":39383,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T16:47:24.000Z","msg":"最後調查一定話用左最低武力, 扮咩跟進緊<br />\n佢地無尊嚴同信譽可言, 為撐而撐, 無人會信佢地<br />\n人地一聽見你係狗隊, 即刻知你咩人格, 咩操行, 咩品德"},{"pid":"4aa8661610d7f58d84a0fc98902ab28f5ae0a319","tid":2203949,"uid":26602,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T16:50:27.000Z","msg":"係唔係港共PR迫班喺到倒米嘅垃圾狗隊做門面嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c85a3c893866befda1fe56d25f62cc0f5dda6678","tid":2203949,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T16:51:11.000Z","msg":"國家完係咪季炳強私人月光杯？"},{"pid":"e380d98efa4328d7aa39989bdf03580189fc7dc9","tid":2203949,"uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T16:52:03.000Z","msg":"condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你啊毅進狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7c63b018d15b44d2ac766591c2cf1e35c07d5b7","tid":2203949,"uid":52459,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T16:56:11.000Z","msg":"呑槍自盡先係認錯的誠意"},{"pid":"502f450c21b73832bae976ae194c4826fab072b3","tid":2203949,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T16:56:58.000Z","msg":"跟進3年之後 冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46cccf89ebc815009a4c22e3cf0de70793c0f90b","tid":2203949,"uid":84116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e0c3374a4f96b15667a7d0654b815343a44e49e","tid":2203949,"uid":39383,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"cited